---

### 9. **ChatOptions (Tool Configuration)**

```csharp
public class ChatOptions {
    // Tools available to the AI model
    public IList<AITool> Tools { get; set; }

    // Control tool call frequency
    public bool AllowMultipleToolCalls { get; set; }

